==When and where it was tested/implemented ==
The ShangRing has been tested in China, Kenya and the United States. It is currently undergoing testing in the latter two countries. It is being used routinely for non-therapeutic, non-preventative circumcision in the United Kingdom [https://www.circumcision-london.co.uk/adult-circumcision/ at this private clinic in London].

